      "title": "5-year multiple entry tourist visa with 6 months stay for 35 countries: Harin",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Cabinet has approved a 5-year multiple entry tourist visa with 6 months stay for 35 countries to help boost tourism in Sri Lanka, Tourism Minister Harin Fernando said.",
        "He said in a twitter post that the decision was taken in addition to the 1-year multiple entry and single entry tourist visas which have 6 months stay period (previously 30 days.)."
